# ui.mdc

- Use TailwindCSS for styling
- Use shadcn/ui components when appropriate
- Use Radix UI primitives for accessible interactions
- Use the cn() utility for class composition
- Build mobile-first responsive layouts
- Prioritize accessibility and keyboard navigation
- Prefer semantic HTML elements
- Use consistent spacing and sizing scales
- Avoid inline styles unless necessary
- Keep visual consistency across components
- Prefer reusable UI primitives
- Avoid excessive animation
- Use loading and empty states where appropriate